"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-australia-news-sport-romanian-prime-minister-boycotts-paris-2024-closing-ceremony-over-gymnastics-medal-controversy-news-story-27452da111f69d0eb7c8e4e9bf3a9496\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Romanian Prime Minister Marcel Ciolacu has announced a boycott of the Paris 2024 Closing Ceremony after gymnast Ana Barbosu had her bronze medal stripped by an appeal from the US gymnastics team.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Romania\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Romanian Prime Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marcel Ciolacu\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\"}, {\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999509047637667, \"rank\": 4.669236014870721e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prime Minister of Romania has cancelled his attendance at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games Closing Ceremony after a Romanian athlete was stripped of her medal.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"score\": 0.9775790844032374, \"rank\": 0.022206639024695655, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9984295876360267, \"rank\": 0.0015517829172125566, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prime Minister Marcel Ciolacu made the announcement on Tuesday after Ana Barbosu had her bronze medal position in gymnastics taken away from her.\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marcel Ciolacu\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barbosu had finished in third place after a stunning floor exercise final but was relegated to fourth by an appeal from the United States gymnastics team.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9997043544697893, \"rank\": 0.0002957130315136595, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u0178\\u2021\\u00b7\\u00f0\\u0178\\u2021\\u00b4\\u00f0\\u0178\\u2021\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u0178\\u2021\\u00b8 Romanian gymnast Ana Barbosu realizing that the successful protest by USA's Jordan Chiles meant that she was pushed from 3rd to 4th place, not getting a medal.Ohh, noooopic.twitter.com/rrYD5dejCn  Mr Ciolacu has described the situation as \\\"scandalous\\\" and \\\"dishonourable\\\" while comparing the incident to Soviet Union corruption.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9984295876360267, \"rank\": 0.0015517829172125566, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999981523550348, \"rank\": 1.3362859696303033e-06, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ciolacu\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\"}, {\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999961416507, \"rank\": 2.868672373828771e-08, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prime Minister said: \\\"I decided not to participate in the closing ceremony of the Paris Olympics after the scandalous situation in gymnastics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To withdraw a medal won through honest hard work on the basis of a challenge, which neither the top coaches nor the top technicians understand, is totally unacceptable!\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember very well how, in communism, the Russians would steal from us at the Olympics, and we'd try to argue with them with no chance of winning.\\\"\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\", \"score\": 0.9715468485970712, \"rank\": 0.02928636884316126, \"text\": \"Russians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The turmoil began when Barbosu, celebrating her bronze medal placement, was blindsided by the news her position had been overturned.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The US gymnastics team made an appeal that Jordan Chiles' routine had been undervalued - and the jury adjusted her score from 13.666 to 13.766.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1618, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999509047637667, \"rank\": 4.669236014870721e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1657, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barbosu had been posing for photos, draped in a Romanian flag, when she was seen collapsing into tears as Chiles was bumped up from fifth place to third.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Romania\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Romanian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Romania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Romanian's distress was palpable as she dropped her national flag and gripped her stomach in shock.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9984295876360267, \"rank\": 0.0015517829172125566, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the event, Prime Minister Ciolacu expressed his outrage: \\\"I could not look at her tears and accept calmly that something like this is perfectly normal!\\\"\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ciolacu\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The fact that hundreds of millions of viewers from all over the world remained, like us Romanians, literally shocked by this terrible scene, shows\\u2026 something is wrong,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2268, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\", \"score\": 0.964067629595394, \"rank\": 0.036890757715207445, \"text\": \"Romanians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to argue with anyone today, but I only choose to protest through my gesture against a blatant injustice.\\\"\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prime Minister announced he would grant Barbosu the Romanian bronze medal prize bonus of \\u20ac21,000 (AU$35,000) even though she officially came fourth.\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2537, \"end\": 2545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9984295876360267, \"rank\": 0.0015517829172125566, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barbosu has since posted on Instagram that her Olympic experience had been \\\"a dream come true\\\".\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2663, \"end\": 2672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1689688704796883e-19, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being in two individual finals was more than I dreamed of.\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going from 8th to 4th in the floor final was exciting!\\\"\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she said.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": []}]}"